These are Puzzles for 4x7 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x7-Level-2-1::.
There 7 different types of food: artichoke, grapes, cabbage, orange, apple, radish, cherry
The people's birthday is in 7 different months: march, october, april, november, july, august, september
City: london, marseilles, colone, miami, berlin, hannover, boston
The people use 7 different means of transport: bike, jet-ski, quad-bike, ship, subway, train, van
 1. the person traveling to miami is on the far right##1
 2. the person traveling to berlin is the person who's birthday is in november##1
 3. the person driving the subway is the person traveling to colone##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left of the person driving the train##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in march is on the right of the person who's birthday is in september##1
 6. the person eating grapes is the person traveling to colone##1
 7. the person driving the van is on the right of the person who's birthday is in july##1
 8. the person driving the ship is between the person driving the van and the person who's birthday is in august##2
 9. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the person driving the quad-bike##1
10. the person eating cabbage is in the middle##1
11. the person traveling to london is the person eating apple##1
12. the person eating apple is the person driving the bike##1
13. the person eating artichoke is on the left of the person who's birthday is in april##1
14. the person who's birthday is in august is the person driving the quad-bike##1
15. the person driving the train is on the left of the person who's birthday is in september##1
16. the person eating grapes is on the left of the person eating radish##1
17. the person traveling to hannover is on the left of the person who's birthday is in april##1
18. the person eating cherry is on the right of the person who's birthday is in july##1
19. the person traveling to boston is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |    3     |     4      |     5     |    6     |    7    |
| Food      | grapes  | radish        | apple | cabbage      | orange     | artichoke      | cherry     |
| Birthday   | october | november         | september   | march | august    | july | april |
| City         | colone | berlin | london | marseilles | boston  | hannover  | miami    |
| Transport     | subway  | train         | bike     | jet-ski    | quad-bike | ship     | van     |

