 1. the person watching comedy movies is the person who growsdahlia##1
 2. the person watching mystery movies is on the left of the person who growsaconite##1
 3. the person driving the ship is on the left of the person watching scientific movies##1
 4. the person who growssunflower is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1
 5. the person driving the ship is on the right of the person who growsmarigold##1
 6. the person watching horror movies is on the left of the person driving the ship##1
 7. the person who growsdaisy is the person watching musical movies##1
 8. the egyptian is the person driving the skateboard##1
 9. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left of the person watching horror movies##1
10. the polish is between the japanese and the person who growsballoon-flower##2
11. the dutch is the person who growsdahlia##1
12. the nigerian is on the left of the british##1
13. the nigerian is between the person who growsballoon-flower and the british##2
14. the person watching musical movies is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
15. the person driving the ship is on the right of the person driving the car##1
16. the person driving the skateboard is on the far left##1
17. the person who growsorchid is on the left of the person watching superhero movies##1
18. the person who growssunflower is on the left of the person who growsmarigold##1
19. the person driving the roller is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
20. the person who growsmarigold is between the person driving the ship and the person who growssunflower##2

