7 different games are played: scrabble, mah-jongg, chess, monopoly, go, canasta, backgammon
The people use 7 different means of transport: helicopter, jet-ski, roller, skateboard, snowmobile, taxi, van
 1. the person driving the taxi is the person traveling to venice##1
 2. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the person playing mah-jongg##1
 3. the person traveling to london is on the far left##1
 4. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the person eating strawberry##1
 5. the person eating kale is on the far left##1
 6. the person eating cauliflower is on the right of the person traveling to san-francisco##1
 7. the person eating strawberry is on the left of the person eating apple##1
 8. the person eating cauliflower is in the middle##1
 9. the person eating broccoli is the person driving the taxi##1
10. the person playing monopoly is on the left of the person driving the taxi##1
11. the person driving the skateboard is the person playing canasta##1
12. the person eating broccoli is on the left of the person traveling to prague##1
13. the person playing mah-jongg is on the right of the person traveling to marseilles##1
14. the person playing chess is on the left of the person eating orange##1
15. the person eating spinach is on the right of the person playing backgammon##1
16. the person traveling to prague is the person playing chess##1
17. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the person playing scrabble##1
18. the person driving the roller is between the person driving the snowmobile and the person driving the jet-ski##2
19. the person traveling to hamburg is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |     2      |     3     |      4       |       5        |      6      |      7      |
